---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Strategy - Bidwell Capital" description="Strategic wealth building through real assets. Cashflow, tax benefits, and long-term appreciation.">
  <section class="hero-sm">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label fade-up fade-up-1">Strategy</span>
      <h1 class="fade-up fade-up-2">Strategic wealth building through real assets</h1>
      <p class="fade-up fade-up-3">We chase cashflow. We chase tax benefits. And we have found that the assets that deliver both also tend to appreciate over time. But we never count on appreciation. Nothing is guaranteed.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Core Philosophy -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="thesis-grid">
        <div>
          <span class="section-label">Investment Thesis</span>
          <h2>Cashflow first. Always.</h2>
          <p>We look for assets we would be happy holding for 10 years or more. Strong cashflow, meaningful tax benefits, strong probability of hitting pro forma, and correlation to larger macro trends. We invest in primary and secondary wealth based in real, tangible assets.</p>
          <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">Most investors are overexposed to equities and underexposed to real assets. We exist to fill that gap. We put money in your pocket every month while building long-term wealth that compounds.</p>
          <p class="disclaimer" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">All investments involve risk, including the possible loss of principal. Past performance is not indicative of future results. Nothing on this website constitutes a guarantee of any return.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
            <h3>Real assets only</h3>
            <p>We understand the layers of wealth and focus on investing in primary and secondary wealth. Commercial real estate credit, multifamily real estate, and energy. Things you can see, touch, and value.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
            <h3>Returns are a premium on risk</h3>
            <p>We leverage personal connections with industry leaders and are constantly trying to be proved wrong. Our underwriting is transparent, simple, and disciplined. We minimize spreadsheet magic.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Investors first</h3>
            <p>Our investors are the priority. We invest our own capital alongside yours. We are operators, not salespeople. Our underwriting and deal flow come from direct operational experience.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Asset Classes -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--bg-secondary);">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">What We Invest In</span>
      <h2>Three asset classes, one philosophy</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">Every asset we invest in must produce income, offer tax advantages, and be backed by something tangible. We look for assets correlated to larger macro trends with a strong probability of hitting pro forma.</p>
      <div class="grid-3">
        <div class="card">
          <span class="badge">Commercial Real Estate Credit</span>
          <h3 style="margin-top: 1rem;">Private Commercial Credit Fund</h3>
          <p style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Preferred equity and mezzanine debt positions across commercial real estate including multifamily, industrial, medical office, and more. Structured with forced sale and take-over rights for downside protection.</p>
          <a href="/track-record" style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.875rem;">View PCCF Dashboard &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <span class="badge">Multifamily Real Estate</span>
          <h3 style="margin-top: 1rem;">Multifamily Syndications</h3>
          <p style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Individual property syndications with direct ownership of multifamily assets. Tax-advantaged through cost segregation and bonus depreciation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <span class="badge">Energy</span>
          <h3 style="margin-top: 1rem;">Oil &amp; Gas Working Interests</h3>
          <p style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Working interest positions in oil and gas. Significant tax deductions through intangible drilling costs, with exposure to a commodity backed by real-world demand and correlated to long-term macro trends.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Core Values -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">What Drives Us</span>
      <h2>Our core values</h2>
      <p style="margin-bottom: 2.5rem;">These are not just words on a wall. They are how we make decisions, evaluate deals, and treat the people we work with.</p>
      <div class="values-grid">
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Liberty</h3>
          <p>True wealth transcends finances. It begins with freedom.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Result driven</h3>
          <p>We demand results from ourselves, our operators, and our investments.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Striving for more</h3>
          <p>We always want to improve. Better underwriting, better communication, better returns.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Investors first</h3>
          <p>Our investors are the priority. Every decision we make starts there.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h3>Enjoyable</h3>
          <p>Building wealth should be rewarding. We believe in having fun along the way.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Founder -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--bg-secondary);">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">About the Founder</span>
      <h2>Adam Penn</h2>
      <p>Software engineer turned real estate operator and fund manager. Adam started his first rental in 2017 while working in tech, eventually building a portfolio of rental properties, a property management company, and launching Bidwell Capital. He is based in Northern California and co-hosts the <a href="https://www.wealthindependencepod.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--accent);">Wealth Independence Podcast</a>.</p>
      <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">This is a first career, not a second act. Adam is a managing partner building and managing assets for decades, not looking for a quick exit. His approach is rooted in engineering: systematic underwriting, data-driven decision making, and a focus on building repeatable, scalable systems. He is building a team around a long-term mission.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero-sm {
    padding: 5rem 0 2rem;
  }

  .hero-sm h1 {
    margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem;
  }

  .hero-sm p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .thesis-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .thesis-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
    }
  }

  .values-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .values-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }

  .values-grid .card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>
